Package WizardTD

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App  
    Enemy
    The Enemy class extends the entity class.
    Entity
    The abstract base class for all entities that have a sprite in the WizardTD.
    Fireball
    The Fireball class is projectile that is fired at a target of the Enemy class.
    Iceball
    The Iceball class extends Fireball and is projectile that is fired at a target of the Enemy class.
    MonsterData
    The MonsterData class stores information about enemies in the game, including their attributes and quantity.
    Wave
    The Wave class represents a wave of monsters in the WizardTD.

    Enum representing game's possible states.
